rong data-start="3019" data-end="3030">DAU/WAU</strong>, <strong data-start="3032" data-end="3055">Playtime por sesi√≥n</strong>, <strong data-start="3057" data-end="3080">Retenci√≥n D1/D7/D30</strong>.</p></li><li data-start="3084" data-end="3138"><p data-start="3086" data-end="3138"><strong data-start="3086" data-end="3099">Fill rate</strong> de salas y tiempo de emparejamiento.</p></li><li data-start="3139" data-end="3187"><p data-start="3141" data-end="3187"><strong data-start="3141" data-end="3155">Conversi√≥n</strong> a pase/skins y uso de emotes.</p></li><li data-start="3188" data-end="3257"><p data-start="3190" data-end="3257"><strong data-start="3190" data-end="3212">Leaderboard health</strong> (varianza; evita dominaci√≥n por ballenas).</p></li></ul><hr data-start="3259" data-end="3262" /><h2 data-start="3264" data-end="3291">Pila t√©cnica recomendada</h2><ul data-start="3293" data-end="3754"><li data-start="3293" data-end="3380"><p data-start="3295" data-end="3380"><strong data-start="3295" data-end="3304">Motor</strong>: Unreal/Unity seg√∫n contenido (nosotros, Unreal + Metahumans para hosts).</p></li><li data-start="3381" data-end="3498"><p data-start="3383" data-end="3498"><strong data-start="3383" data-end="3394">Netcode</strong>: replicaci√≥n ligera + <strong data-start="3417" data-end="3433">relay WebRTC</strong> para voice/chat; servidores dedicados para modos competitivos.</p></li><li data-start="3499" data-end="3594"><p data-start="3501" data-end="3594"><strong data-start="3501" data-end="3512">Backend</strong>: microservicios (matchmaking, perfiles, econom√≠a); <strong data-start="3564" data-end="3573">cache</strong> para leaderboards.</p></li><li data-start="3595" data-end="3675"><p data-start="3597" data-end="3675"><strong data-start="3597" data-end="3607">Escala</strong>: contenedores + autoscaling; CDN para assets; logs centralizados.</p></li><li data-start="3676" data-end="3754"><p data-start="3678" data-end="3754"><strong data-start="3678"